executor_description: Add a file or directory to IPFS.

queryParams.description: The path to a file to be added to IPFS.
Use trickle-dag format for dag generation.
Only chunk and hash - do not write to disk.
Wrap files with a directory object.
Include files that are hidden. Only takes effect on recursive add. chunker [string]: Chunking algorithm to use.
Pin this object when adding. The default is true.
Use raw blocks for leaf nodes. (Experimental)
Check the filestore for pre-existing blocks. (Experimental)
Cid version. Non-zero value changes the default of raw-leaves to true. The default is 0. (Experimental)
Hash function to use. Sets cid-version to 1 if used. The default is sha2-256. (Experimental)
Add directory paths recursively. The default is false.
